OL,3,CMan, 76, charged after children fell
OL,4,Cill at Leicestershire summer camp
OL,6,FA man has been charged after a number
OL,7,Fof children fell ill at a summer camp
OL,8,Fin Leicestershire.
OL,10,FJohn Ruben, 76, of Landmere Lane,
OL,11,FRuddington, Nottingham, has been
OL,12,Fcharged with three counts of wilful
OL,13,Fill treatment of a child.
OL,15,FHe was originally arrested on
OL,16,Fsuspicion of intentionally poisoning
OL,17,Fthe children at a summer camp in
OL,18,FStathern in Leicestershire.
