OL,3,CMan, 76, charged after children fell
OL,4,Cill at Leicestershire summer camp
OL,6,FThe charges relate to three different
OL,7,Fchildren on Sunday (27 July) that
OL,8,Fchildren at a summer camp being held
OL,9,Fat Stathern Lodge in Canal Lane,
OL,10,FStathern, near Melton, had become
OL,11,Funwell.
OL,13,FLeicestershire Police received a
OL,14,Freport on Sunday after children became
OL,15,Funwell at a camp in Stathern.
