OL,3,CMan, 76, charged after children fell
OL,4,Cill at Leicestershire summer camp
OL,6,FEast Midlands Ambulance Service
OL,7,Fassessed the children on Monday 28
OL,8,FJuly. Eight children and one adult
OL,9,Fwere taken to the Queen's Medical
OL,10,FCentre in Nottingham and later
OL,11,Fdischarged.
OL,13,FA man was arrested at a nearby public
OL,14,Fhouse on Monday evening.
OL,16,FRuben has been remanded into custody
OL,17,Fand will appear at Leicester
OL,18,FMagistrates' Court tomorrow.
