OL,3,CMan, 76, charged after children fell
OL,4,Cill at Leicestershire summer camp
OL,6,FThe owners and operators of Stathern
OL,7,FLodge are independent from those
OL,8,Fpeople who use or hire the lodge and
OL,9,Fare not connected to the incident.
OL,11,FJanine McKinney, Chief Crown
OL,12,FProsecutor for CPS East Midlands,
OL,13,Fsaid: "The Crown Prosecution Service
OL,14,Fhas authorised the prosecution of a 76-
OL,15,Fyear-old man with child cruelty
OL,16,Foffences following a police
OL,17,Finvestigation into a summer camp held
OL,18,Fat Stathern Lodge, Leicestershire.
