OL,3,CMan, 76, charged after children fell
OL,4,Cill at Leicestershire summer camp
OL,6,F"This decision has been made after
OL,7,Freviewing a file of evidence from
OL,8,FLeicestershire Police.
OL,10,F"Jonathon Ruben will be charged with
OL,11,Fthree child cruelty offences relating
OL,12,Fto three boys. He will appear at
OL,13,FLeicester Magistrates' Court on
OL,14,FSaturday, 2 August.
OL,16,F"This has been an extremely upsetting
OL,17,Fand shocking moment for the community,
OL,18,Fand especially for the children and
OL,19,Fparents most directly affected.
