OL,6,F"We would like to remind all concerned
OL,7,Fthat there are now active criminal
OL,8,Fproceedings against Mr Ruben, and he
OL,9,Fhas the right to a fair trial. There
OL,10,Fmust be no reporting, commentary or
OL,11,Fsharing of information online that may
OL,12,Fin any way prejudice these
OL,13,Fproceedings."
